text: "Anything Is Possible" is a 1990 song by Debbie Gibson and is the title track to her third studio album Anything Is Possible. It went to number 26 in the United States, number 51 in the United Kingdom, number 17 in Canada and number 60 in Australia. ==Track listings== ==References== Category:1990 songs Category:Dance-pop songs Category:Debbie Gibson songs
title: Anything Is Possible (Debbie Gibson song)
